<p><i><b>The Blistering Sun</b></i> is <a href="/wiki/Rachael_Sage" title="Rachael Sage">Rachael Sage</a>'s seventh album, released in 2006.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Track_listing">Track listing</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Blistering_Sun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Track listing">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>All songs written by <a href="/wiki/Rachael_Sage" title="Rachael Sage">Rachael Sage</a> unless otherwise indicated.</p>
<ol>
<li>"Alright, OK" – 3:47</li>
<li>"Featherwoman" – 3:47</li>
<li>"93 Maidens" – 2:56</li>
<li>"Wildflower" – 3:40</li>
<li>"Violet or Blue" – 4:18</li>
<li>"Lonely Streets" – 3:25</li>
<li>"Older" – 4:56</li>
<li>"Hit Song" – 2:42</li>
<li>"Burning Witch" – 5:03</li>
<li>"Paperplane" – 3:57</li>
<li>"Proof" – 3:41</li>
<li>"Surprise" – 4:40</li>
<li>"Anything Anywhere" (<a href="/wiki/Melissa_Ferrick" title="Melissa Ferrick">Melissa Ferrick</a>) – 4:23</li>
<li>"C'mon Over" – 5:14</li>
<li>"Calypso" – 5:27</li>
</ol>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Personnel">Personnel</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Blistering_Sun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Personnel">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Rachael_Sage" title="Rachael Sage">Rachael Sage</a> – <a href="/wiki/Vocals" title="Vocals" class="mw-redirect">vocals</a>, <a href="/wiki/Piano" title="Piano">piano</a>, <a href="/wiki/Celesta" title="Celesta">celeste</a>, <a href="/wiki/Mellotron" title="Mellotron">Mellotron</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wurlitzer" title="Wurlitzer">Wurlitzer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Harpsichord" title="Harpsichord">electric harpsichord</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Edie_Carey&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Edie Carey (page does not exist)">Edie Carey</a> – <a href="/wiki/Backing_vocals" title="Backing vocals" class="mw-redirect">backing vocals</a> on 2 11</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Doug_Yowell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Doug Yowell (page does not exist)">Doug Yowell</a> – <a href="/wiki/Drum_kits" title="Drum kits" class="mw-redirect">drums</a> on 1-4 6 7 11 12 14</li>
