<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Conrad_Korsch&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Conrad Korsch (page does not exist)">Conrad Korsch</a> – bass on 8-10 13</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Todd_Sickafoose" title="Todd Sickafoose">Todd Sickafoose</a> – bass on 15, <a href="/wiki/Percussion_instrument" title="Percussion instrument">percussion</a> on 15</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ben_Butler_(musician)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Ben Butler (musician) (page does not exist)">Ben Butler</a> – <a href="/wiki/Guitar" title="Guitar">guitars</a> on 2-4 12 14</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Jack_Petruzelli&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Jack Petruzelli (page does not exist)">Jack Petruzelli</a> – guitar on 5 7 9 10</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Russ_Johnson_(musician)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Russ Johnson (musician) (page does not exist)">Russ Johnson</a> – <a href="/wiki/Trumpet" title="Trumpet">trumpet</a>, <a href="/wiki/Flugelhorn" title="Flugelhorn">flugelhorn</a> on 1 3-6 8-10 12 14</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Allison_Cornell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Allison Cornell (page does not exist)">Allison Cornell</a> – <a href="/wiki/Violin" title="Violin">violin</a>, <a href="/wiki/Viola" title="Viola">viola</a> on 3 5 7</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Julia_Kent" title="Julia Kent">Julia Kent</a> – <a href="/wiki/Cello" title="Cello">cello</a> on 4 7 9-11 15</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Julie_Wolf&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Julie Wolf (page does not exist)">Julie Wolf</a> – <a href="/wiki/Organ_(music)" title="Organ (music)">organ</a> on 13 14</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Dave_Eggar" title="Dave Eggar">Dave Eggar</a> – cello on 3 13</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Marianne_Osiel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Marianne Osiel (page does not exist)">Marianne Osiel</a> – <a href="/wiki/Flute" title="Flute">flute</a>, <a href="/wiki/Oboe" title="Oboe">oboe</a> on 3 4 6 7</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Rob_Curto&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Rob Curto (page does not exist)">Rob Curto</a> – organ, <a href="/wiki/Accordion" title="Accordion">accordion</a> on 3 4 6 7</li>
</ul>
